---
title: BBQ Cherry-Glazed Chicken & Slaw with Sweetcorn & Crushed Potato Salad
description: Vegetarians don’t need to miss out on the smokey flavours of the American South with this flavour-packed BBQ and cherry-glazed chicken, plus all the fixins (including a sweetcorn and potato salad)! Enjoy a taste of the good ol’ USA right here.

